name: Bastards #1
description: Bastards, is an entitlement of Harmony in Chaos and disorder angst with hellish anger. Represented through audio-reactive visuals generated through fractal and noise. Using self-produced music using samples from drum loops and traditional Indonesian gamelan under the moniker mnemonik in soundcloud. it is an expression of banging noises and hatred towards everything represented through ambient and dissonant voices as audio.
